OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773435971
OL,3,CMPs criticise Fujitsu for not
OL,4,Ccontributing 'a penny' to Post Office
OL,5,Credress
OL,7,FA group of MPs has hit out at Fujitsu
OL,8,Ffor being "yet to contribute a penny"
OL,9,Fto the nearly #1.5 billion redress
OL,10,Fbill for victims of the Post Office
OL,11,FHorizon scandal.
OL,13,FThe Business and Trade Committee
OL,14,F(BTC), which scrutinises the work of
OL,15,Fthe government department, said it had
OL,16,Ffound "serious structural failings" in
OL,17,Fthe compensation process.
OL,19,FThey also called for urgent action to
OL,20,Fquash the pre-Horizon convictions.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@eO]xD@GOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
