OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773435971
OL,3,CMPs criticise Fujitsu for not
OL,4,Ccontributing 'a penny' to Post Office
OL,5,Credress
OL,7,FA spokeswoman for Fujitsu said: "We
OL,8,Fcontinue to work with UK government to
OL,9,Fensure we adhere to the voluntary
OL,10,Frestrictions we put in place regarding
OL,11,Fbidding for new contracts while the
OL,12,FPost Office Inquiry is ongoing, and
OL,13,Fare engaged with government regarding
OL,14,FFujitsu's contribution to
OL,15,Fcompensation."
