CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773435971
OL,3,CMPs criticise Fujitsu for not
OL,4,Ccontributing 'a penny' to Post Office
OL,5,Credress
OL,7,FA spokeswoman for the Post Office said
OL,8,Fit would review the committee's
OL,9,Frecommendation and continue to work
OL,10,Fclosely with the government.
OL,12,FShe said: "We welcome the scrutiny of
OL,13,Fthe committee and its commitment to
OL,14,Fensuring full, fair and timely redress
OL,15,Fis paid to those harmed during the
OL,16,FHorizon scandal.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
