CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773435971
OL,3,CMPs criticise Fujitsu for not
OL,4,Ccontributing 'a penny' to Post Office
OL,5,Credress
OL,7,F"Progress has been made with 87% of
OL,8,Feligible Horizon Shortfall Scheme
OL,9,Fapplications having received an offer
OL,10,Fand #882 million paid through the
OL,11,Fscheme.
OL,13,F"We are processing applications as
OL,14,Fquickly as possible to bring
OL,15,Fresolution to those who have applied."
OL,17,FA spokeswoman for the government said:
OL,18,F"We must never lose sight of the
OL,19,FHorizon scandal's human impact on
OL,20,Fpostmasters and their families."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@fO]zD@AOU
